{"id":592704,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/08/【昨日重现】文三娃：关于竞技体育，闲话两句/","date":"2018-08-12T15:41:24Z","modified":"2018-08-13T08:08:10Z","title":"【昨日重现】文三娃：关于竞技体育 闲话两句","content":"<p><b>“体育局里都是蛀虫，我国的体育就毁在你们这帮人手里！”</b></p>\n<p><b>  ———— 马哈维亚·辛格·珀尕 （印）</b></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_001-5.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-592662\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_001-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"230\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_001-5.jpg 1076w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_001-5-300x125.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_001-5-768x321.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_001-5-1024x428.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>也是曾经的“体育人”，毕业进国家体委（我现在的法定身份信息，还关联在崇文区体育馆路），当年一起入职培训的小伙小丫们，现在不少已是总局机关或各个中心挑大梁的骨干了。</p>\n<p>机关报干了几年，此后又在市场化的体育媒体做过近10年。体育圈水深水浑，但也分程度。</p>\n<p>最透明最干净的恰恰是最不争气的足球，尽管因假球黑哨被抓被判那么多。</p>\n<p>像一些有奥运优势的冷门小众项目，特别是穷人家女孩子扎堆的重竞技（举柔摔等）中长跑等，领奖台那一刹那的辉煌，掩盖了多少肮脏的交易与丑陋的背叛。运动员与教练员之间的故事，可不是像《摔跤吧！爸爸》那样虽然挫折但仍富有节奏美感。</p>\n<p class=\"text\">我的个人经历，也有这么灰色的一段。</p>\n<p class=\"text\">初中时为参加重庆市青少年运动会，户口被改小了一岁（最后还没选拔上），这是人生第一次作弊。</p>\n<p class=\"text\">中国体育看上去很美，但我总不惮以最大的恶意去想象它。最悲哀的是，它根本不在乎，没有任何丑闻能击倒它，何况猜忌。</p>\n<p><b>延伸阅读</b></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.360doc.com/content/17/1212/01/36068027_712271892.shtml\">寻找迷失的队伍——孙英杰兴奋剂事件之后</a></p>\n<p>竞技体育的目标是更快更高更强，共产主义的理想是世界大同乌有之乡。<br />\n分开吧，都是特别瑰丽美好的事情。<br />\n偏偏，共产国际看上了竞技体育……<br />\n从此开启了互害模式的文体苦旅。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_002-4.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-592663\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_002-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"713\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_002-4.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_002-4-231x300.jpg 231w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>有人觉得我几句话说通透了，也有人觉得啥也没说。</p>\n<p>2017年中刘国梁被解除总教练职务，国乒陆续出现消极比赛甚至罢赛，公众大哗。</p>\n<p>风波中的刘国梁这洋洋洒洒一大片像啥都说了，又像啥也没说。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_003-4.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-592664\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_003-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"1365\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_003-4.jpg 934w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_003-4-121x300.jpg 121w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_003-4-768x1906.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_003-4-413x1024.jpg 413w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>这就是敝国竞技体育的常态， get used to it, you folks.</p>\n<p>2017年的12月初，关于田亮的的一则旧闻成了头条。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_004-5.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-592665\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_004-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"693\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_004-5.jpg 762w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_004-5-238x300.jpg 238w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sports.163.com/17/1206/22/D50OM6NR00058782.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">最高检披露体坛丑闻：田亮被内定最高8.5分</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>大约从20年前开始，我就与跳水和体操开始了亲密接触——时任《中国体育报》这两个项目的专项记者。</p>\n<p>体育报是国家体委机关报，我在体育队的身份自然特别，再加上年龄比当时国家队主力队员大不了几岁，交流非常顺畅。</p>\n<p>除了比赛，国家队的休闲度假、酒会晚会、甚至包括军训等活动，都会邀请我参加。</p>\n<p>与队伍的关系太好，也有个问题，当教练之间，运动员之间，教练和运动员之间出现矛盾冲突时，他们会希望我有倾向性的态度。</p>\n<p>把你当了朋友，几近无话不说，我倾听了很多故事，了解了很多情绪，这时候自己的记者身份就非常尴尬了。</p>\n<p>后来因为一定程度上坚持了所谓专业主义、搞什么劳什子的平衡报道，把体操队甚至跳水队的各个派系的重点人物几乎得罪光了。</p>\n<p><b>“当年那么对你，现在这样写我。”</b></p>\n<p>这真是一件悲伤的事。</p>\n<p>大陆竞技优势热门项目，跟新闻联播似的，美闻太多，丑闻太少，所谓内幕被制度化地层层包裹，既然如此隔膜，更加上不想把得罪过的人再得罪一次，也不想扒开自己曾经的伤口再撒一把盐，干脆无话可说。</p>\n<p>那就发照片吧。</p>\n<p>聊以纪念——我与他们曾经的青春。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_592666\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_005-3.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592666\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_005-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_005-3.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_005-3-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_005-3-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_005-3-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">曾经的男子体操梦之队</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592667\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_006-4.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592667\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_006-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_006-4.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_006-4-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_006-4-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_006-4-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">与中国体操队队长李小双</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592668\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_007-4.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592668\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_007-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_007-4.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_007-4-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_007-4-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_007-4-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">与中国体操队队长张津京</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592669\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_008-4.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592669\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_008-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"735\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_008-4.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_008-4-224x300.jpg 224w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_008-4-768x1027.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_008-4-766x1024.jpg 766w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">与中国体操女队队长刘璇</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592670\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_009-3.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592670\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_009-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_009-3.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_009-3-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_009-3-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_009-3-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">探望在中国人民大学就读的体操世界冠军莫慧兰</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592671\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_010-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592671\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_010-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_010-2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_010-2-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_010-2-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_010-2-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">莫慧兰</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592672\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_011-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592672\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_011-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_011-2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_011-2-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_011-2-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_011-2-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">客串了一阵刘璇的业余摄影师</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592673\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_012-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592673\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_012-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_012-2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_012-2-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_012-2-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_012-2-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">莫慧兰与刘璇</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592674\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_013-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592674\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_013-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_013-2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_013-2-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_013-2-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_013-2-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">莫慧兰、奎媛媛与体操小将们</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592675\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_014-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592675\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_014-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_014-2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_014-2-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_014-2-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_014-2-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">与体操世界冠军毕文静</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592676\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_015-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592676\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_015-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_015-2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_015-2-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_015-2-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_015-2-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">与奥运体操选手吉丽雅</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592677\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_016-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592677\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_016-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_016-2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_016-2-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_016-2-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_016-2-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">与女子体操世界冠军奎媛媛</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592678\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_017-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592678\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_017-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_017-2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_017-2-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_017-2-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_017-2-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">国家体操队军训。中间是中国体操金童玉女李小鹏和刘璇</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592679\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_018-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592679\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_018-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_018-2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_018-2-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_018-2-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_018-2-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">下图：体操女队队长刘璇与军训士兵</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592680\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_019-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592680\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_019-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_019-2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_019-2-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_019-2-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_019-2-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">世界冠军奎媛媛在军训中</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592681\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_020-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592681\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_020-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"735\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_020-2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_020-2-224x300.jpg 224w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_020-2-768x1027.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_020-2-766x1024.jpg 766w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">与体操运动员桑兰</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592682\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_021-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592682\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_021-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_021-2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_021-2-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_021-2-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_021-2-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">中国女子体操三朵金花：奎媛媛、刘璇、毕文静</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592683\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_022-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592683\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_022-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_022-2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_022-2-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_022-2-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_022-2-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">左起：体操中心副主任高健、男队队长张津京、中心主任张健、李宁、女队代理队长凌洁</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592684\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_023-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592684\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_023-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_023-2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_023-2-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_023-2-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_023-2-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">99年天津世锦赛，中国体操大家庭聚会</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592685\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_024-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592685\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_024-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_024-2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_024-2-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_024-2-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_024-2-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">与鞍马奥运冠军李东华</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592686\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_025-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592686\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_025-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_025-2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_025-2-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_025-2-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_025-2-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">与国家体操队总教练黄玉斌</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>与中国跳水队的渊源</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_592687\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_026-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592687\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_026-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_026-2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_026-2-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_026-2-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_026-2-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">1999年，与奥运冠军田亮在峨眉山</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592688\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_027-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592688\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_027-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_027-2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_027-2-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_027-2-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_027-2-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">我也来了一张。摄影：田亮</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592689\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_028-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592689\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_028-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_028-2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_028-2-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_028-2-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_028-2-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">与田亮恩师张挺</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592690\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_029-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592690\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_029-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_029-2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_029-2-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_029-2-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_029-2-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">采访郭晶晶和伏明霞</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592691\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_030-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592691\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_030-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_030-2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_030-2-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_030-2-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_030-2-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">与奥运冠军郭晶晶</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592692\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_031-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592692\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_031-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_031-2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_031-2-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_031-2-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_031-2-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">中国跳水队。左一郭晶晶，右一田亮，时称跳水界金童玉女。</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592693\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_032-1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592693\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_032-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_032-1.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_032-1-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_032-1-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_032-1-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">备战悉尼奥运会的国家队队员黄强，右边为胡佳</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>黄强原是田亮的双人跳搭档，90年代末，以近乎完美的技术条件知名（有著名教练称黄强天资超过了一哥田亮），所谓俄罗斯跳水沙皇“萨乌丁”唯一克星。性格外向，极机灵，不安分，经常违反队规。</p>\n<p>出于一些不可言说的原因，田亮的奥运搭档换成了胡佳。</p>\n<p>黄强这颗曾经被伯乐们寄予无限希望的天才，从此一蹶不振。</p>\n<p>我个人亦非常欣赏黄强，也一度与他交好。后本人换了采访项目，渐渐疏远。多年后在一次全运会上再见，他连地方队的主力都混不上，泯然众人矣。</p>\n<p>而黄强最近的消息，更是令我这个早已失联的老友，唏嘘不已。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.114nba.com/view-46-109606.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">前中国跳水世界冠军黄强 被控健身房强奸20岁马国女运动员</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_592694\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_033.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592694\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_033.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_033.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_033-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_033-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_033-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">2000年，备战悉尼奥运会的田亮</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_592695\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_034-1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592695\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_034-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_034-1.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_034-1-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_034-1-768x575.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_034-1-1024x766.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">三位功勋教练</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>这张图片里的三位教练，左一钟少珍，郭晶晶教练，中间张挺，田亮教练，最右周继红，中国跳水队领队。</p>\n<p>与这三位著名教练都曾有非常好的交情，他们的故事，单独说都非常美好、励志，揉在一起讲，会产生难以名状的化学反应。</p>\n<p>那就不讲了。</p>\n<p>就看看照片吧。</p>\n<p>偶尔能情不自禁想起这些可爱的人，也刻意去忘掉那些不可爱的事。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>尾声</strong></p>\n<p class=\"text\">我的第一份工作是在CRI（中国国际广播电台）担任英语播音，毕竟有国际新闻的教育背景，也算专业对了口。</p>\n<p class=\"text\">在国际台还未转正，就“跳槽”到了中国体育报，成了体育专业记者，这界在外人看来，跨得有点猝不及防。</p>\n<p>天坛东门，体育馆路，也成了我北漂生活的原点。</p>\n<p>2015年底失业至今，为了寻找档案和办理社保，不得不一次又一次地回到这里。</p>\n<p>​<b>延伸阅读</b></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wentommy.wordpress.com/2018/04/29/%e9%98%91%e5%b0%be%e4%b8%8e%e6%a1%a3%e6%a1%88/\">阑尾与档案</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_592696\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_035-1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592696\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_035-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"735\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_035-1.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_035-1-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">体育报社外的地铁站</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>90年代末分配到国家体委，没几年就离开了。</p>\n<p>因户口落在这里，但凡办点需要开证明的事儿，都不得不回来。</p>\n<p>每次都盼着是最后一次。</p>\n<p>但不得不一次次回到这里，跟西部世界接待员一般的宿命轮回。</p>\n<p>当年翩翩少年，今已大腹便便，捧一老头儿杯，轻车熟路鬼使神差，一下子就找到了老单位的开水间。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_592697\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_036-1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-592697\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_036-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"735\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_036-1.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_036-1-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">2018年6月27日，为办社保补开的离职证明</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>十年砍柴曾调侃，当年我从北师大毕业不去中国新闻学院的话，现在应该至少是一中学或职业学院校长了。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_037-1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-592698\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_037-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"160\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_037-1.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_037-1-300x88.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_037-1-768x224.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_037-1-1024x299.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>也有网友分析，若当年留在体委系统，​怕也是躲不过加官进爵的宿命。</p>\n<p>不是没当官的命，而是对走仕途本能排斥。</p>\n<p><b>延伸阅读</b></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wentommy.wordpress.com/2017/07/20/%e8%8b%a5%e6%9c%89%e6%9d%a5%e7%94%9f%e4%b8%8d%e5%81%9a%e5%ae%98/\">若有来生不做官</a></p>\n<p>话说回来，千禧年时我就被组织派到四川当记者站站长了。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_038-1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-592699\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_038-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_038-1.jpg 1400w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_038-1-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_038-1-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_038-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>在进入体委系统前，我也并非与体育毫无渊源。</p>\n<p class=\"text\">中学期间就曾练过三年射击——气手枪和小口径手枪。</p>\n<p class=\"text\">个子虽小（一米五九），幸运地有了点运动天赋，除了射击，也开发出了中长跑的潜质，400米能轻轻松松跑进一分以内，高一时拿了校运会冠军，把同学们吓了一跳，后来分班时一度成了班主任们争抢的对象——指着我在运动会上拿成绩呢。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_040-1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-592701\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_040-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"735\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_040-1.jpg 700w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_040-1-224x300.jpg 224w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p class=\"text\">体质最好的那会儿，我的跳远成绩达到过6米30。</p>\n<p class=\"text\">一度因此加强了训练，想跳到6米50的三级运动员标准，实现高考加分。</p>\n<p class=\"text\">但毕竟还是有能力天花板，跳到6米以上的次数都不多，根本无法突破，只好放弃。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_592700\" style=\"width: 709px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_039-1.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-592700\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_039-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"699\" height=\"523\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_039-1.jpg 699w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_039-1-300x224.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">在中国新闻学院参加运动会</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"text\">但就凭了这点身体素质，在学生时代拿来赚点同学们惊奇与喝彩，还是绰绰有余的。</p>\n<p class=\"text\">记得刚上北师大那会儿，系里组织篮球比赛，我也报了名，从大伙儿的眼神儿里我能读出这样的信息：四川小板凳儿也真是自不量力，玩儿篮球，这不自取其辱么。</p>\n<p class=\"text\">我们班在哲学系的篮球水平是最差的，可以说所有的比赛时间都是垃圾时间，别说外班外系的女生了，就是本班的女生，都不大好意思来加油助威。</p>\n<p class=\"text\">嫌寒碜。</p>\n<p class=\"text\">输得实在太惨，对方进了10个我们连1个球没有，上谁不上谁，都没关系了。</p>\n<p class=\"text\">“小六子，你去玩儿吧！”</p>\n<p class=\"text\">我在宿舍排行老六，跟小学、中学情况一样，个子又是全班最矮。</p>\n<p class=\"text\">场面发生了戏剧性变化，在东北山东大汉丛里，这个1米59的“小六子”如入无人之境，防守队员刚追过半场，我这已经三步上篮，稳稳得分了。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_042-1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-592703\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_042-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"933\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_042-1.jpg 700w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_042-1-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_592702\" style=\"width: 709px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_041-1.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-592702\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_041-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"699\" height=\"1053\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_041-1.jpg 699w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_041-1-199x300.jpg 199w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/pic_041-1-680x1024.jpg 680w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">大一，北师大校园</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"text\">北师大92级的军训放在大二，昌平阳坊。</p>\n<p class=\"text\">同学们已经见怪不怪了，倒是军训教官们，对我的跑跳投、匍匐前进，对了还有射击等方面表现出的能力大吃了好几惊。</p>\n<p class=\"text\">要是当年两山轮战还未结束，再加上被哪个首长凑巧看到，我没准儿就被部队扣下了。</p>\n<p class=\"text\">不过，正所谓“好汉不提当年勇”，体能体质这玩意儿，用进废退，过了学生时代，跟年龄增长成反比，也是自然规律。</p>\n<p class=\"text\">当年浑身上下都是爆发力的“小鲜肉”，现在的体能状况，大概是这样子的。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://new-play.tudou.com/v/451649408.html?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">参座健身视频</a></p>\n<p>健身啊，盆友们。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1056,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,9203],"tags":[14306,20266,28824,30593,35677]}